WITH metadata AS (
    SELECT value
    FROM jsonb_array_elements($projectpulse040_metadata$[["001","For the ones with Custom, Organization-wide time operations: view time entries for Engineering and Project Management users; approve or reject submitted time; move or reassign time entries between authorized projects, tasks, and work items; correct time on behalf of users with a required reason; maintain full audit history. No permanent deletion, user impersonation, system configuration, or unaudited changes.","https://github.com/ahmedadeyemi-cts/project-time-platform/blob/main/docs/MODULE-CATALOG.md"],["002","For the ones with Custom, Organization-wide delegated approval authority: view the full approval workflow and approval history; approve or reject at the Project Team Coordinator stage; approve on behalf of a Manager; approve on behalf of a Project Manager; return time for correction; and move items between valid approval stages. Every delegated action must record the required approval stage, original responsible role/person, acting PTC, reason, previous status, new status, timestamp, and immutable audit history. This authority applies to time-approval workflows only and does not include password-reset approvals, deletion of approval history, user impersonation, system configuration, or unaudited changes.","https://github.com/ahmedadeyemi-cts/project-time-platform/blob/main/docs/MODULE-CATALOG.md"],["003","For the ones with Custom, View utilization data in read-only mode for self and the role-authorized team or user scope. Editing utilization records, targets, formulas, or system configuration is not permitted. Access must respect the configured team, management, project-team, or organization scope and must not expose unrelated users.","https://github.com/ahmedadeyemi-cts/project-time-platform/blob/main/docs/MODULE-CATALOG.md"],["004","","https://github.com/ahmedadeyemi-cts/project-time-platform/blob/main/docs/MODULE-CATALOG.md"],["005","","https://github.com/ahmedadeyemi-cts/project-time-platform